# Cloning remote repository and verifying pre-commit hook

- git clone git@github.com:alixnamoussart/git-hooks-nodejs.git git-hooks-nodejs-from-remote
- no node_modules
- no pre-commit in .git/hooks
- install npm packages that are in package.json: jest and pre-commit: <mark>npm install is enough</mark> => installs pre-commit in .git/hooks, install all necessary npm modules
- change mult module, add, commit => failure
- pre-commit NPM package doesn't support other Git hooks except pre-commit hook

